e chain.\n+\n+## OUTPUT CONTRACT\n+\n+Produce exactly three artifacts. Canonical state/delta record must include iteration/run 3, route proof, novelty, status/focus/count, questions, ruled-out directions, tools/sources, timestamp/duration, optional graphEvents, and executor provenance for `cli-opencode` / `openai/gpt-5.6-sol-fast`. Do not edit config, strategy, registry, dashboard, or research.md.\n","additions":53,"deletions":0}],"diagnostics":{},"truncated":false},"title":"Success. Updated the following files:\nA .opencode/specs/sk-design/012-style-database-and-interface-commands/007-gap-remediation-research/001-restructure/research/lineages/sol-high-fast/prompts/iteration-003.md","time":{"start":1784617076440,"end":1784617076444}},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"fc_094e433495ca4994016a5f18608bb08191a3c10ab751b06653"}},"id":"prt_f8377393d001q2kKOPwVvCFvfy","sessionID":"ses_07c97d905ffee2yzbow793KIc8","messageID":"msg_f837727eb00107iWihcsKfPiBD"}}
