ffeyzpX3nXvfJV9mJ\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_f83878825001k0mRNeCkAb2z6t\",\"messageID\":\"msg_f838765af001YdfOZIFQOVZO9J\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_07c7f8618ffeyzpX3nXvfJV9mJ\",\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Iteration 4 produced exactly three artifacts:\\n\\n- `iterations/iteration-004.md`\\n- `deltas/iter-004.jsonl`\\n- Appended `deep-research-state.jsonl`\\n\\nKey outcomes:\\n\\n- Two runnable mixed-state migration boundaries.\\n- Manifest-driven, shell-safe move for exactly 1,290 bundles.\\n- Oracle subtree assigned entirely to `tests/oracle/`.\\n- `style-library.mjs` and `operator.mjs` preserved without speculative wrappers.\\n- Mutable database artifacts excluded from source migration.\\n- Exact move groups, compatibility policy, verification ladder, and rollback boundary documented.\\n\\nValidation passed:\\n\\n- Both JSONL files parse successfully.\\n- State ends at iteration/run 4.\\n- `git diff --check` passed.\\n- No source files, reducer outputs, config, strategy, registry, dashboard, or `research.md` were modified.\\n- Iteration 5 remains mandatory.\",\"time\":{\"start\":1784618125349,\"end\":1784618132726},\"metadata\":{\"openai\":{\"itemId\":\"msg_02d1df4f8ab4870b016a5f1c8d38548191b5c0e41a7baad2b2\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}}}}\n{\"type\":\"step_finish\",\"timestamp\":1784618133235,\"sessionID\":\"ses_07c7f8618ffeyzpX3nXvfJV9mJ\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_f8387a6f2001GIZ67neFelzSI2\",\"reason\":\"stop\",\"snapshot\":\"ad3d555169e7760a1f355bb5558688b8c1648169\",\"messageID\":\"msg_f838765af001YdfOZIFQOVZO9J\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_07c7f8618ffeyzpX3nXvfJV9mJ\",\"type\":\"step-finish\",\"tokens\":{\"total\":145079,\"input\":4919,\"output\":187,\"reasoning\":197,\"cache\":{\"write\":0,\"read\":139776}},\"cost\":0}}\n","exit":0,"truncated":true,"outputPath":"/Users/michelkerkmeester/.local/share/opencode/tool-output/tool_f83810feb001zrnsQyAP1x7XBM"},"title":"env -i HOME=\"$HOME\" PATH=\"$PATH\" LANG=\"$LANG\" TMPDIR=\"$TMPDIR\" USER=\"$USER\" LOGNAME=\"$LOGNAME\" OPENAI_API_KEY=\"${OPENAI_API_KEY:-}\" AI_SESSION_CHILD=1 MK_SPEC_GATE_ENFORCE=0 opencode run --model openai/gpt-5.6-sol-fast --format json --dangerously-skip-permissions --pure --dir \"$PWD\" \"$(<'.opencode/specs/sk-design/012-style-database-and-interface-commands/007-gap-remediation-research/001-restructure/research/lineages/sol-high-fast/prompts/iteration-004.md')\" </dev/null","time":{"start":1784618133236,"end":1784618133733}},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"fc_0a8eba2ff3a7e463016a5f1abad31081918459e7ff41e8da42"}},"id":"prt_f838069ef001B7kNjrL4MVqD2k","sessionID":"ses_07c97d905ffee2yzbow793KIc8","messageID":"msg_f83805a45001WNTboEReLfudU3"}}
