l-safe `git mv` plan.\n+Audit and adjudicate the complete target tree and migration plan before synthesis.\n \n ## Active Risks\n \n - Detached-lineage safety requires shared spec writeback, parent-resolving reducer calls, memory save, and git staging to remain deferred.\n-- Oracle ownership is contradictory across iterations 2 and 3 and needs an exact-import adjudication before synthesis.\n+- Oracle ownership contradiction is resolved by exact imports in iteration 4: all current oracle consumers are tests.\n+- Audit the 1,290-source move for command-length and partial-failure behavior before finalizing.\n","additions":9,"deletions":4}],"diagnostics":{},"truncated":false},"title":"Success. Updated the following files:\nM .opencode/specs/sk-design/012-style-database-and-interface-commands/007-gap-remediation-research/001-restructure/research/lineages/sol-high-fast/deep-research-strategy.md\nM .opencode/specs/sk-design/012-style-database-and-interface-commands/007-gap-remediation-research/001-restructure/research/lineages/sol-high-fast/findings-registry.json\nM .opencode/specs/sk-design/012-style-database-and-interface-commands/007-gap-remediation-research/001-restructure/research/lineages/sol-high-fast/deep-research-dashboard.md","time":{"start":1784618187169,"end":1784618187179}},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"fc_08beb99368d66c24016a5f1ca86c5c8191a88e592e653307ba"}},"id":"prt_f8387f203001u0vtriKInaSSgo","sessionID":"ses_07c97d905ffee2yzbow793KIc8","messageID":"msg_f8387d469001cZkFJ1obEsP8sA"}}
