\\\":\\\"correction\\\",\\\"iteration\\\":5,\\\"id\\\":\\\"mutable-database-policy\\\",\\\"summary\\\":\\\"No sk-design ignore or mutable DB exists; ignore database/* except README and probe style-library.sqlite.current.json.\\\"}\\n{\\\"type\\\":\\\"finding\\\",\\\"iteration\\\":5,\\\"id\\\":\\\"documentation-link-inventory\\\",\\\"summary\\\":\\\"Rewrite the 1,290 root-relative styles README links plus active skill, catalog, playbook, mode, generator, and packet docs.\\\"}\\n{\\\"type\\\":\\\"ruled_out\\\",\\\"iteration\\\":5,\\\"approach\\\":\\\"Chunked or per-source bundle moves\\\",\\\"reason\\\":\\\"The one-process argv is far below ARG_MAX and avoids additional partial-failure boundaries and ordering complexity.\\\"}\",\"truncated\":false,\"loaded\":[],\"display\":{\"type\":\"file\",\"path\":\"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.worktrees/0093-sk-design-012-gap-research/.opencode/specs/sk-design/012-style-database-and-interface-commands/007-gap-remediation-research/001-restructure/research/lineages/sol-high-fast/deltas/iter-005.jsonl\",\"text\":\"{\\\"type\\\":\\\"iteration\\\",\\\"iteration\\\":5,\\\"run\\\":5,\\\"mode\\\":\\\"research\\\",\\\"target_agent\\\":\\\"deep-research\\\",\\\"agent_definition_loaded\\\":true,\\\"resolved_route\\\":\\\"Resolved route: mode=research target_agent=deep-research execution=single_iteration state_source=externalized_files do_not_switch_mode=true\\\",\\\"newInfoRatio\\\":0.44,\\\"noveltyJustification\\\":\\\"Three findings are new corrections (measured argv safety, missing generator gate, and absent mutable-state ignores), while four adjudications consolidate or sharpen prior inventory and ownership evidence.\\\",\\\"status\\\":\\\"complete\\\",\\\"focus\\\":\\\"Final conformance audit, contradiction resolution, inventory completeness, command safety, and implementation-ready adjudication.\\\",\\\"findingsCount\\\":7,\\\"keyQuestions\\\":[\\\"Do all tracked sources, tests, consumers, manifest