{"type":"text","timestamp":1784618866040,"sessionID":"ses_07c97d905ffee2yzbow793KIc8","part":{"id":"prt_f83927f69001rciIEbM0Hb6TQo","messageID":"msg_f839254cc001m8IX4ija28EM8X","sessionID":"ses_07c97d905ffee2yzbow793KIc8","type":"text","text":"## Objective\n- Complete a detached five-iteration deep-research lineage for restructuring `.opencode/skills/sk-design/styles/`, then synthesize an implementation-ready target layout, migration path, and `git mv` plan.\n\n## Important Details\n- Write only inside `/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.worktrees/0093-sk-design-012-gap-research/.opencode/specs/sk-design/012-style-database-and-interface-commands/007-gap-remediation-research/001-restructure/research/lineages/sol-high-fast`.\n- Session: `fanout-sol-high-fast-1784616068213-1azjys`; executor/model: `cli-opencode` / `openai/gpt-5.6-sol-fast`; stop policy: `max-iterations`.\n- Final response must be exactly `FANOUT_LINEAGE_COMPLETE:sol-high-fast`.\n- Shared spec writeback, memory save, git staging, and reducer commands resolving the parent packet remain deferred because they write outside the authorized lineage.\n- Final architecture retains `library/{bundles,manifests}`, `lib/{engine,database}`, `scripts/`, `database/`, `tests/`, and `docs/`; no old-path aliases or speculative CLI wrappers.\n- Preserve production filenames one-for-one; oracle code is entirely test-owned. Mutable database names must follow actual `style-library.sqlite*` conventions.\n- Iteration 5 identified corrections involving bundle-move argv safety, a missing generator verification gate, and absent mutable-state ignore coverage.\n\n## Work State\n### Completed\n- Loaded deep-research workflow, protocol, state, convergence, agent, and `cli-opencode` contracts.\n- Initialized lineage-local config, JSONL state, strategy, registry, dashboard, prompts, iterations, deltas, and lock.\n- Completed and validated all five iterations with `verify-iteration.cjs`:\n  - Iteration 1: current topology and consumers, `newInfoRatio=0.89`.\n  - Iteration 2: runtime transfer rules, `0.88`.\n  - Iteration 3: target tree, `0.88`; succeeded after one allowed retry.\n  - Iteration 4: dependency order and exact move plan, `0.86`.\n  - Iteration 5: final audit/adjudication, `0.44`.\n- Manually synchronized strategy, registry, and dashboard through iteration 4.\n- Confirmed the source tree was not modified.\n\n### Active\n- Iteration 5 findings still need incorporation into strategy, registry, and dashboard.\n- `research.md`, final lifecycle state, config completion status, and final validation remain outstanding.\n\n### Blocked\n- Audited dispatcher failed before launch with `ERR_MODULE_NOT_FOUND` for `runtime/lib/deep-loop/jsonl-repair.js`; direct documented `opencode run` dispatch was used instead.\n- No current blocker.\n\n## Next Move\n1. Read the remainder of `iterations/iteration-005.md`, incorporate its adjudications into reducer-owned lineage files, and synthesize `research.md`.\n2. Validate JSON/JSONL and all artifacts, append completion lifecycle state, mark config complete, release `.deep-research.lock`, then output the exact completion marker.\n\n## Relevant Files\n- `/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.worktrees/0093-sk-design-012-gap-research/.opencode/specs/sk-design/012-style-database-and-interface-commands/007-gap-remediation-research/001-restructure/research/lineages/sol-high-fast/`: authorized artifact root.\n- `/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.worktrees/0093-sk-design-012-gap-research/.opencode/specs/sk-design/012-style-database-and-interface-commands/007-gap-remediation-research/001-restructure/research/lineages/sol-high-fast/iterations/iteration-005.md`: final audit requiring synthesis.\n- `/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.worktrees/0093-sk-design-012-gap-research/.opencode/specs/sk-design/012-style-database-and-interface-commands/007-gap-remediation-research/001-restructure/research/lineages/sol-high-fast/deep-research-state.jsonl`: append-only state with five iteration records.\n- `/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.worktrees/0093-sk-design-012-gap-research/.opencode/specs/sk-design/012-style-database-and-interface-commands/007-gap-remediation-research/001-restructure/research/lineages/sol-high-fast/deep-research-strategy.md`: strategy synchronized through iteration 4.\n- `/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.worktrees/0093-sk-design-012-gap-research/.opencode/specs/sk-design/012-style-database-and-interface-commands/007-gap-remediation-research/001-restructure/research/lineages/sol-high-fast/findings-registry.json`: registry synchronized through iteration 4.\n- `/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.worktrees/0093-sk-design-012-gap-research/.opencode/specs/sk-design/012-style-database-and-interface-commands/007-gap-remediation-research/001-restructure/research/lineages/sol-high-fast/deep-research-dashboard.md`: dashboard synchronized through iteration 4.\n- `/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.worktrees/0093-sk-design-012-gap-research/.opencode/specs/sk-design/012-style-database-and-interface-commands/007-gap-remediation-research/gap-analysis.md`: confirmed parent evidence.\n- `/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.worktrees/0093-sk-design-012-gap-research/.opencode/commands/deep/assets/deep-research-auto.yaml`: governing workflow.","time":{"start":1784618844009,"end":1784618866039},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"msg_0977ffa4a40a5513016a5f1f5bf5a081918a114e3dbe4077ae","phase":"final_answer"}}}}
