{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1784619019987,"sessionID":"ses_07c97d905ffee2yzbow793KIc8","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"grep","callID":"call_ItnDN3PfLdAFFAyXUhS4g4F9","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"pattern":"^## ","path":"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.worktrees/0093-sk-design-012-gap-research/.opencode/specs/sk-design/012-style-database-and-interface-commands/002-research-design-commands/research/lineages/sol/research.md"},"output":"Found 100 matches (more matches available)\n/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.worktrees/0093-sk-design-012-gap-research/.opencode/specs/sk-design/012-style-database-and-interface-commands/002-research-design-commands/research/lineages/sol/deep-research-strategy.md:\n  Line 3: ## 2. TOPIC\n\n  Line 7: ## 3. KEY QUESTIONS (remaining)\n\n  Line 16: ## 4. NON-GOALS\n\n  Line 22: ## 5. STOP CONDITIONS\n\n  Line 28: ## 6. ANSWERED QUESTIONS\n\n  Line 39: ## 7. WHAT WORKED\n\n  Line 45: ## 8. WHAT FAILED\n\n  Line 51: ## 9. EXHAUSTED APPROACHES (do not retry)\n\n  Line 300: ## 10. RULED OUT DIRECTIONS\n\n  Line 354: ## 10A. SATURATED DIRECTIONS AND DIVERGENCE FRONTIER\n\n  Line 365: ## 11A. CARRIED-FORWARD OPEN QUESTIONS\n\n  Line 382: ## 11. NEXT FOCUS\n\n  Line 388: ## 12. KNOWN CONTEXT\n\n  Line 394: ## 13. RESEARCH BOUNDARIES\n\n\n/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.worktrees/0093-sk-design-012-gap-research/.opencode/specs/sk-design/012-style-database-and-interface-commands/002-research-design-commands/research/lineages/sol/resource-map.md:\n  Line 11: ## Summary\n\n\n/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.worktrees/0093-sk-design-012-gap-research/.opencode/specs/sk-design/012-style-database-and-interface-commands/002-research-design-commands/research/lineages/sol/iterations/iteration-010.md:\n  Line 3: ## Focus\n\n  Line 6: ## Findings\n\n  Line 13: ## Prompt Template\n\n  Line 18: ## Ruled Out\n\n  Line 22: ## Assessment\n\n  Line 26: ## Recommended Next Focus\n\n\n/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.worktrees/0093-sk-design-012-gap-research/.opencode/specs/sk-design/012-style-database-and-interface-commands/002-research-design-commands/research/lineages/sol/iterations/iteration-004.md:\n  Line 3: ## Focus\n\n  Line 6: ## Actions Taken\n\n  Line 11: ## Findings\n\n  Line 18: ## Questions Answered\n\n  Line 21: ## Questions Remaining\n\n  Line 25: ## Ruled Out\n\n  Line 30: ## Assessment\n\n  Line 34: ## Reflection\n\n  Line 39: ## Recommended Next Focus\n\n\n/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.worktrees/0093-sk-design-012-gap-research/.opencode/specs/sk-design/012-style-database-and-interface-commands/002-research-design-commands/research/lineages/sol/iterations/iteration-011.md:\n  Line 3: ## Focus\n\n  Line 6: ## Findings\n\n  Line 13: ## Prompt Template\n\n  Line 18: ## Ruled Out\n\n  Line 22: ## Assessment\n\n  Line 26: ## Recommended Next Focus\n\n\n/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.worktrees/0093-sk-design-012-gap-research/.opencode/specs/sk-design/012-style-database-and-interface-commands/002-research-design-commands/research/lineages/sol/iterations/iteration-007.md:\n  Line 3: ## Focus\n\n  Line 6: ## Actions Taken\n\n  Line 11: ## Findings\n\n  Line 19: ## Questions Answered\n\n  Line 22: ## Questions Remaining\n\n  Line 25: ## Ruled Out\n\n  Line 30: ## Assessment\n\n  Line 34: ## Reflection\n\n  Line 39: ## Recommended Next Focus\n\n\n/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.worktrees/0093-sk-design-012-gap-research/.opencode/specs/sk-design/012-style-database-and-interface-commands/002-research-design-commands/research/lineages/sol/iterations/iteration-006.md:\n  Line 3: ## Focus\n\n  Line 6: ## Actions Taken\n\n  Line 11: ## Findings\n\n  Line 19: ## Questions Answered\n\n  Line 23: ## Questions Remaining\n\n  Line 26: ## Ruled Out\n\n  Line 31: ## Assessment\n\n  Line 35: ## Reflection\n\n  Line 40: ## Recommended Next Focus\n\n\n/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.worktrees/0093-sk-design-012-gap-research/.opencode/specs/sk-design/012-style-database-and-interface-commands/002-research-design-commands/research/lineages/sol/iterations/iteration-020.md:\n  Line 3: ## Focus\n\n  Line 6: ## Final Recommendation\n\n  Line 17: ## Converged Architecture\n\n  Line 27: ## Implementation Order\n\n  Line 35: ## Acceptance Gates\n\n  Line 45: ## Residual Risks\n\n  Line 51: ## Eliminated Alternatives\n\n  Line 54: ## Assessment\n\n  Line 58: ## Stop Decision\n\n\n/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.worktrees/0093-sk-design-012-gap-research/.opencode/specs/sk-design/012-style-database-and-interface-commands/002-research-design-commands/research/lineages/sol/iterations/iteration-017.md:\n  Line 3: ## Focus\n\n  Line 6: ## Findings\n\n  Line 13: ## Rollout Sequence\n\n  Line 20: ## Ruled Out\n\n  Line 25: ## Assessment\n\n  Line 29: ## Recommended Next Focus\n\n\n/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.worktrees/0093-sk-design-012-gap-research/.opencode/specs/sk-design/012-style-database-and-interface-commands/002-research-design-commands/research/lineages/sol/iterations/iteration-015.md:\n  Line 3: ## Focus\n\n  Line 6: ## Findings\n\n  Line 13: ## Responsibility Matrix\n\n  Line 22: ## Ruled Out\n\n  Line 27: ## Assessment\n\n  Line 31: ## Recommended Next Focus\n\n\n/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.worktrees/0093-sk-design-012-gap-research/.opencode/specs/sk-design/012-style-database-and-interface-commands/002-research-design-commands/research/lineages/sol/iterations/iteration-019.md:\n  Line 3: ## Focus\n\n  Line 6: ## Findings\n\n  Line 13: ## Example Paths\n\n  Line 22: ## Ruled Out\n\n  Line 27: ## Assessment\n\n  Line 31: ## Recommended Next Focus\n\n\n/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.worktrees/0093-sk-design-012-gap-research/.opencode/specs/sk-design/012-style-database-and-interface-commands/002-research-design-commands/research/lineages/sol/iterations/iteration-001.md:\n  Line 3: ## Focus\n\n  Line 6: ## Actions Taken\n\n  Line 11: ## Findings\n\n  Line 17: ## Questions Answered\n\n  Line 20: ## Questions Remaining\n\n  Line 24: ## Ruled Out\n\n  Line 27: ## Dead Ends\n\n  Line 30: ## Assessment\n\n  Line 34: ## Reflection\n\n  Line 39: ## Recommended Next Focus\n\n\n/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.worktrees/0093-sk-design-012-gap-research/.opencode/specs/sk-design/012-style-database-and-interface-commands/002-research-design-commands/research/lineages/sol/iterations/iteration-016.md:\n  Line 3: ## Focus\n\n  Line 6: ## Test Matrix\n\n  Line 22: ## Findings\n\n  Line 29: ## Ruled Out\n\n  Line 34: ## Assessment\n\n  Line 38: ## Recommended Next Focus\n\n\n/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.worktrees/0093-sk-design-012-gap-research/.opencode/specs/sk-design/012-style-database-and-interface-commands/002-research-design-commands/research/lineages/sol/iterations/iteration-005.md:\n  Line 3: ## Focus\n\n  Line 6: ## Actions Taken\n\n  Line 11: ## Findings\n\n\n(Results truncated. Consider using a more specific path or pattern.)","metadata":{"matches":100,"truncated":true},"title":"^## ","time":{"start":1784619019972,"end":1784619019986}},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"fc_0ebf94ead88945b8016a5f200a8e3081918ad5c55a05e8715a"}},"id":"prt_f8395295b001EHytRCC41Zgr2W","sessionID":"ses_07c97d905ffee2yzbow793KIc8","messageID":"msg_f8395170f001aIMhiG2qY5Ra5h"}}
